                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-constable. I heard the alarm as I was going down Rupert-street - the prisoner and the portmanteau were given to me; I found 5s. 8 1/2d. on him - he seemed very sorry.</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded poverty.</p>
